1
00:00:02,900 --> 00:00:06,900
"KÔKÔ KYÔSHI"

2
00:00:13,700 --> 00:00:18,400
<i>Haru no komorebi no
naka de</i>

3
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:21,700
<i>What about the life
expectancy?</i>

4
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:24,700
<i>Only five percent of patients
of this disease survive.</i>

5
00:00:24,700 --> 00:00:26,560
<i>I'd say six months at most.</i>

6
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:28,560
<i>It's a warm color.</i>

7
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:31,660
<i>I'm not really dying, am I?</i>

8
00:00:31,660 --> 00:00:34,530
<i>I'm only 17.</i>

9
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:42,800
<i>At that point I don't think
I understood the purpose</i>

10
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:45,000
<i>of my "experiment".</i>

11
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,180
<i>Why?</i>

12
00:00:48,180 --> 00:00:50,650
<i>Because it wasn't true.</i>

13
00:00:50,650 --> 00:00:56,880
<i>I was going to tell her.</i>

14
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:03,400
<i>To explain that it wasn't her who
was going to die - it was me.</i>

15
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,300
Stand.

16
00:01:05,300 --> 00:01:07,700
Bow. Sit.

17
00:01:07,700 --> 00:01:09,700
<i>This girl's fate isn't the same
as mine.</i>

18
00:01:09,700 --> 00:01:13,100
<i>What lies in her future?
I don't love you anymore.</i>

19
00:01:13,100 --> 00:01:18,270
<i>When I'm in love,
I wanted it to last forever.</i>

20
00:01:18,270 --> 00:01:21,710
<i>I'm sorry. It's true.</i>

21
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:24,240
<i>You're going to...</i>

22
00:01:25,750 --> 00:01:28,480
Of course I don't go
to host clubs!

23
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:33,060
Don't misunderstand.
We're not trying to punish you.

24
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:37,200
I understand that a girl your
age wants to experience

25
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:39,360
different things.

26
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:41,930
You're being quite lenient.

27
00:01:41,930 --> 00:01:46,970
That's right. Usually what you did
would be grounds for expulsion.

28
00:01:46,970 --> 00:01:48,740
Thank Fujimura<i>-sensei.</i>

29
00:01:48,740 --> 00:01:51,900
You're just scared
of my parents, right?

30
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:54,700
They contribute so much
to the school.

31
00:01:56,510 --> 00:01:59,080
Money can't buy you
respectability.

32
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:03,520
If students stop coming to our
school, there is no more school.

33
00:02:05,850 --> 00:02:09,320
We can't afford these kinds
of distractions.

34
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:12,190
Next time, we won't be
so understanding.

35
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:15,030
Are you threatening me?

36
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:17,970
Why not try and follow
the rules?

37
00:02:26,070 --> 00:02:30,200
Sorry about that girl
in my class.

38
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:33,300
Corporal punishment doesn't have
a place in schools today.

39
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:34,450
Of course not.

40
00:02:34,450 --> 00:02:38,820
But that doesn't mean
you can't discipline them.

41
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:44,060
If you aren't firm,
they'll walk all over you.

42
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:47,290
I'm sorry.

43
00:02:51,570 --> 00:02:55,640
- Could I have some, too?
- Sure.

44
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:59,570
"If you aren't firm,
they'll walk all over you."

45
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:05,350
There used to be this teacher
I hated.

46
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:10,320
He was a gym teacher.

47
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:14,490
What a moron.

48
00:03:14,490 --> 00:03:17,030
But...

49
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:20,000
Now I sound just like him.

50
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,430
Strange, huh?

51
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:24,730
Still, I'm sure she won't
go back.

52
00:03:24,730 --> 00:03:26,700
Thanks.

53
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:31,710
Somehow I don't think that host
will give up so easily.

54
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:35,510
He knows that she's rich.

55
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:39,610
That's why he's after her.

56
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:46,290
You seem to be enjoying
yourself.

57
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:49,760
After a while,
just teaching gets boring.

58
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:52,000
You know?

